        <dict>
            <key>NSTemporaryExceptionAllowsInsecureHTTPLoads</key>
            <true/>
        </dict>
    </dict>
</dict>Run the Packager ## From the root of your project, where the `node_modules` directory is located.
$ npm startRun the App #If you are using Xcode or your favorite editor, build and run your native iOS application as normal. Alternatively, you can run the app from the command line using:# From the root of your project
